1. caseとifを使わないで関数を作りましょう

~~~ {.haskell}
analysisLine' :: String -> String
analysisLine' []   = "empty"
analysisLine' [_]  = "a character"
analysisLine' s'
  | last s' == '.' = "a sentence"
  | ' ' `elem` s'  = "some words"
  | otherwise      = "a word"
~~~

